WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 25=

01:39.020 --> 01:39.900
How has he treated you

01:40.490 --> 01:41.410
these past half a month?

01:44.540 --> 01:45.570
He's treated me

01:47.660 --> 01:48.500
well.

01:52.210 --> 01:53.380
And how do you feel about him?

01:58.050 --> 01:58.890
I...

02:00.770 --> 02:02.210
Do you like him?

02:11.940 --> 02:13.100
I do.

02:14.890 --> 02:16.500
When I broke off the engagement with Yuqi,

02:17.410 --> 02:18.690
I didn't feel sad.

02:21.220 --> 02:22.500
But when I think

02:23.660 --> 02:25.820
that I might never see Mu Qingyan again,

02:28.820 --> 02:30.540
my heart feels empty,

02:33.380 --> 02:34.220
it hurts.

02:40.170 --> 02:41.010
Zhao,

02:42.260 --> 02:43.980
now that your engagement is dissolved,

02:44.260 --> 02:45.260
in principle,

02:45.660 --> 02:46.820
who you choose to be with

02:47.060 --> 02:48.290
is up to you.

02:48.780 --> 02:49.850
If that boy truly is

02:50.260 --> 02:51.690
a child of the Chang family,

02:51.890 --> 02:53.500
your mother and I would be very pleased.

02:53.500 --> 02:54.370
But

02:54.410 --> 02:55.250
don't forget,

02:56.100 --> 02:57.780
he is the young master of the demon sect.

02:58.130 --> 02:58.970
What of it?

03:00.130 --> 03:02.170
Are there any fewer vile people
among the Six Sects?

03:04.690 --> 03:06.690
There are plenty of vile people
in the Six Sects.

03:06.890 --> 03:08.220
Yin Dai is the first that comes to mind.

03:08.540 --> 03:09.410
And that Wang Yuanjing,

03:09.730 --> 03:11.290
he deserves to die ten times over.

03:12.100 --> 03:12.940
But Zhao,

03:13.730 --> 03:14.570
is Mu Qingyan

03:14.780 --> 03:15.890
necessarily a good man?

03:16.510 --> 03:17.850
You forgot the story your master told you

03:17.850 --> 03:18.850
about the skin-painted demon?

03:18.850 --> 03:20.340
Mu Qingyan may not be that demon.

03:20.820 --> 03:21.780
And didn't your aunt

03:21.780 --> 03:23.610
once think the same?

03:31.890 --> 03:32.850
What do you mean?

03:37.850 --> 03:38.980
Mother?

03:39.820 --> 03:41.730
This concerns your aunt's reputation.

03:42.290 --> 03:44.340
If you weren't facing the same situation now,

03:44.340 --> 03:46.060
we would have taken this secret to our graves.

03:52.660 --> 03:53.500
Back then,

03:54.010 --> 03:55.890
your aunt, your master,

03:56.730 --> 03:57.780
and your Uncle Lei,

03:58.170 --> 03:59.340
seven of them in all,

04:00.730 --> 04:02.060
secretly trained in a formation

04:02.060 --> 04:04.170
derived from the Big Dipper Formation.

04:05.170 --> 04:06.220
Once completed,

04:06.660 --> 04:08.340
even Nie Hengcheng would have struggled
against it.

04:08.780 --> 04:10.010
But unexpectedly,

04:10.500 --> 04:11.780
aside from your master and your aunt,

04:12.130 --> 04:13.130
the other five

04:13.610 --> 04:14.660
were ambushed

04:14.660 --> 04:15.540
before the final battle.

04:16.220 --> 04:18.050
Your Uncle Lei survived,

04:18.250 --> 04:20.220
but was left crippled for life.

04:20.900 --> 04:22.850
The place where the seven of them hid,

04:22.850 --> 04:24.050
aside from themselves,

04:24.370 --> 04:25.780
only one other person knew.

04:27.730 --> 04:28.570
The skin-painted demon?

04:30.610 --> 04:32.660
So the cold case Uncle Tieqiao mentioned

04:33.900 --> 04:35.250
was his doing?

04:36.050 --> 04:37.540
Now you understand why your aunt

04:38.290 --> 04:39.370
charged off without hesitation

04:39.370 --> 04:41.170
to kill Nie Hengcheng back then.

04:41.660 --> 04:42.780
That demon had caused the deaths

04:43.250 --> 04:45.490
of the brothers who shared life and death
with her.

04:45.490 --> 04:46.390
How could her heart

04:46.400 --> 04:47.410
not be torn apart?

04:47.900 --> 04:48.930
With the formation ruined,

04:50.410 --> 04:51.780
she had no choice

04:53.140 --> 04:54.810
but to face the demon alone.

04:55.900 --> 04:58.050
Your aunt was killed by the skin-painted demon.

05:00.220 --> 05:01.370
Where did he go afterward?

05:02.050 --> 05:03.660
Your aunt only said he disappeared.

05:04.370 --> 05:06.020
We know nothing more.

05:11.170 --> 05:12.010
Zhao,

05:13.730 --> 05:15.020
you've always had a mind of your own.

05:16.700 --> 05:17.810
Learn from the past,

05:18.980 --> 05:21.020
don't follow in your aunt's footsteps.

05:34.780 --> 05:36.930
Remember what your master told you:

05:37.250 --> 05:38.100
a demon

05:39.290 --> 05:40.850
will devour people.

05:41.140 --> 05:42.780
Mu Qingyan may not be that demon.

05:43.170 --> 05:44.140
And didn't your aunt

05:44.140 --> 05:45.850
once think the same?

06:18.540 --> 06:20.020
(Nie Zhe has appeared in the Hanhai Mountains.)

06:20.390 --> 06:21.700
(There may be clues about the man in black.)

06:21.700 --> 06:22.540
(Three days from now,)

06:22.780 --> 06:23.620
(I'll wait for you.)

06:23.930 --> 06:24.850
Zhao.

06:24.850 --> 06:26.020
Learn from the past,

06:27.020 --> 06:29.050
don't follow in your aunt's footsteps.

06:45.410 --> 06:46.370
(No need to wait.)

06:47.340 --> 06:49.050
(I'll find the man in black myself.)

06:50.220 --> 06:51.610
(The martial world has no set meeting.)

06:52.140 --> 06:53.540
(Mr. Mu, take care.)

07:06.490 --> 07:07.330
Milady,

07:07.610 --> 07:09.220
why aren't you eating?

07:09.540 --> 07:10.380
I'm not hungry.

07:11.370 --> 07:12.210
Milady,

07:12.610 --> 07:14.220
don't take those vile rumors

07:14.220 --> 07:15.930
outside to heart.

07:15.930 --> 07:18.930
It was clearly Mu Qingyan's
one-sided infatuation.

07:18.930 --> 07:20.020
When he was at Qingque Sect,

07:20.020 --> 07:20.900
I could tell

07:20.900 --> 07:22.410
he was always clinging to you.

07:22.410 --> 07:24.290
He is handsome, I'll grant him that,

07:24.290 --> 07:25.410
but

07:25.410 --> 07:26.300
I never imagined

07:26.320 --> 07:27.780
he'd dare harbor improper thoughts about you.

07:27.780 --> 07:28.620
Zhao.

07:32.340 --> 07:33.290
Zhuo.

07:33.290 --> 07:34.130
Xingjia.

07:38.610 --> 07:40.490
I'll go brew some tea.

07:48.730 --> 07:49.570
Zhao,

07:50.140 --> 07:51.250
I roasted a chicken,

07:51.540 --> 07:52.380
cumin-flavored.

07:53.290 --> 07:54.130
Have a taste.

07:54.540 --> 07:56.100
I truly have no appetite.

08:00.730 --> 08:05.020
"My belt grows loose, yet I do not regret."

08:05.020 --> 08:08.540
"For him, I grow haggard and worn."

08:14.220 --> 08:15.610
Have you two lost your minds?

08:16.980 --> 08:17.830
Zhao, we've thought it

08:17.900 --> 08:18.740
over again and again.

08:19.170 --> 08:20.340
Why not

08:21.490 --> 08:22.330
forget about him?

08:23.850 --> 08:25.290
Whether he's good or bad,

08:25.660 --> 08:27.660
our master and your parents will never agree.

08:27.900 --> 08:29.170
It's too hard.

08:29.850 --> 08:31.490
Have you two nothing better to do?

08:33.130 --> 08:34.530
If you follow Young Master Mu

08:34.530 --> 08:36.180
and someday we stand on opposite sides
of a battle,

08:36.180 --> 08:37.980
how are we supposed to face each other?

08:38.370 --> 08:40.820
But if you marry Yuzhi instead,

08:41.370 --> 08:43.100
the Six Sects of Beichen,

08:43.100 --> 08:45.220
or at least three or four of them

08:45.220 --> 08:47.250
could ensure mutual security
and advance together.

08:47.250 --> 08:48.820
Old grudges could be resolved as well.

08:49.580 --> 08:50.530
Wouldn't that be ideal?

08:51.010 --> 08:52.850
I'll go see how Feicui's tea is coming along.

08:53.820 --> 08:54.890
The chicken is all yours.

08:56.730 --> 08:58.850
The ancestors of the Song family

08:59.250 --> 09:01.010
have finally shown their favor.

09:02.850 --> 09:03.770
This rascal

09:04.180 --> 09:06.300
has finally come to his senses.

09:12.220 --> 09:13.370
Only the timing

09:13.720 --> 09:14.570
may not be ideal.

09:14.610 --> 09:15.450
How so?

09:16.010 --> 09:18.010
Right now, Zhao and that Mu boy

09:18.010 --> 09:19.610
are the talk of the entire city.

09:20.060 --> 09:21.770
If he proposes at this moment,

09:21.770 --> 09:23.580
people will surely gossip.

09:24.370 --> 09:25.210
And none of it

09:26.100 --> 09:27.060
will sound pleasant.

09:27.060 --> 09:28.300
That's precisely why

09:29.180 --> 09:31.300
he must propose now.

09:35.580 --> 09:36.420
Good.

09:36.770 --> 09:37.730
That's responsibility.

09:37.730 --> 09:39.530
A true son of the Song family.

09:50.220 --> 09:51.060
The keys to

09:51.370 --> 09:52.210
the storeroom,

09:52.420 --> 09:53.260
the treasure chests,

09:53.420 --> 09:55.420
the accounts office, and over a hundred estates

09:55.770 --> 09:56.610
are all here.

09:58.770 --> 10:00.300
Over a hundred estates?

10:00.300 --> 10:01.140
Easy.

10:04.100 --> 10:05.650
Lord Song, are you truly

10:05.650 --> 10:07.100
going to propose for your son?

10:07.100 --> 10:08.730
Such a serious matter,

10:08.730 --> 10:09.730
how could it be a joke?

10:09.730 --> 10:11.250
Rest assured,

10:11.250 --> 10:12.890
if Zhao marries into our Guangtian Sect,

10:12.890 --> 10:14.730
she will never suffer the slightest grievance.

10:14.980 --> 10:15.820
Yes, yes, of course.

10:15.980 --> 10:17.010
Though I have two sons,

10:17.340 --> 10:19.730
everyone knows I favor the younger one.

10:20.060 --> 10:21.580
His future wife would be

10:21.770 --> 10:22.640
the one in charge

10:22.700 --> 10:24.220
in Guangtian Sect.

10:25.490 --> 10:26.340
Yes,

10:26.370 --> 10:28.220
everyone knows you have a favorite.

10:29.130 --> 10:30.220
But isn't it a bit soon

10:30.220 --> 10:31.300
to propose now?

10:31.500 --> 10:32.340
Yes, yes.

10:32.340 --> 10:33.770
What about Mu Qingyan?

10:34.100 --> 10:34.940
What did you say?

10:35.060 --> 10:36.010
She mentioned Mu Qingyan.

10:38.610 --> 10:40.650
It is perfectly normal

10:40.650 --> 10:43.060
for a pretty young girl to have one or two

10:43.060 --> 10:44.010
unreliable admirers.

10:44.700 --> 10:45.650
That's good to hear.

10:48.740 --> 10:49.580
Truth be told,

10:49.580 --> 10:50.460
Yuzhi is

10:50.530 --> 10:51.370
a good boy.

10:51.650 --> 10:52.490
I like him.

10:52.860 --> 10:53.730
But the problem is

10:53.730 --> 10:55.850
Zhao just broke off an engagement.

10:55.850 --> 10:58.010
To get betrothed again immediately...

10:58.010 --> 10:58.850
Enough.

10:59.420 --> 11:00.490
Pingchun,

11:00.940 --> 11:02.850
you've roamed the martial world for years.

11:03.010 --> 11:04.650
Haven't you heard the saying:

11:04.890 --> 11:06.700
"A good girl has a hundred suitors"?

11:06.700 --> 11:07.540
Isn't that right?

11:09.120 --> 11:09.980
Stop reading.

11:09.980 --> 11:11.420
Say something.

11:11.730 --> 11:12.570
Yunke.

11:14.220 --> 11:15.370
Yunke.

11:15.980 --> 11:16.980
Say something.

11:17.300 --> 11:19.420
Zhao and Yuzhi are a match made in heaven,

11:22.820 --> 11:23.660
aren't they?

11:24.010 --> 11:25.100
If they marry,

11:25.250 --> 11:26.580
what could those people in

11:26.730 --> 11:27.740
the martial world possibly say?

11:29.010 --> 11:29.980
They are indeed

11:29.980 --> 11:30.980
a good match.

11:32.300 --> 11:34.820
But Zhao has always had a mind of her own.

11:35.130 --> 11:37.370
She's just ended her engagement with Yuqi,

11:37.610 --> 11:38.810
and now to promise her to someone else...

11:39.010 --> 11:41.490
I fear she may not agree.

11:41.890 --> 11:43.060
Let the young

11:43.250 --> 11:45.220
handle their own affairs.

11:45.820 --> 11:47.650
Rest easy.

12:29.700 --> 12:31.340
Tri-colored peach blossoms?

12:48.850 --> 12:50.300
Yuzhi, why did you ask me here,

12:51.300 --> 12:52.700
and in such

12:53.530 --> 12:55.100
a mysterious way?

12:55.530 --> 12:56.370
Zhao,

12:57.100 --> 12:58.060
I asked you here because

12:58.700 --> 12:59.940
there's something I must tell you.

13:12.730 --> 13:14.300
My father has asked Mr. Cai to let you
marry me.

13:14.770 --> 13:16.250
But I need your consent.

13:18.340 --> 13:19.220
You and me?

13:21.610 --> 13:23.220
Lord Song is being utterly reckless.

13:24.100 --> 13:25.420
That was my wish.

13:27.060 --> 13:27.900
Zhao,

13:29.420 --> 13:30.420
I care for you deeply.

13:44.730 --> 13:45.580
I know.

13:45.890 --> 13:47.610
Yuzhi, you want to help me out of
this predicament.

13:48.770 --> 13:49.610
But I don't need that.

13:50.180 --> 13:51.130
Aunt once said,

13:51.850 --> 13:53.060
in life there are

13:53.420 --> 13:55.370
hardships that you must face them yourself,

13:55.770 --> 13:56.850
and no one can shoulder for you.

13:57.650 --> 13:58.580
In the end,

13:58.580 --> 13:59.540
we can only rely on ourselves.

14:00.610 --> 14:02.130
I don't want to be a coward anymore,

14:05.490 --> 14:06.420
hiding behind you

14:06.850 --> 14:08.250
under the guise of marriage,

14:09.010 --> 14:10.420
letting you bear the blame.

14:12.130 --> 14:12.970
That wouldn't be fair.

14:13.420 --> 14:14.260
Zhao,

14:14.940 --> 14:16.220
I'm not trying to rescue you.

14:16.490 --> 14:17.700
Thank you for your kindness, Yuzhi.

14:18.250 --> 14:19.300
In my heart,

14:19.770 --> 14:21.340
you will always be the best senior brother.

14:28.490 --> 14:29.330
In that case,

14:30.010 --> 14:31.700
you still owe me a bowl of

14:32.010 --> 14:32.980
lotus congee.

14:54.530 --> 14:55.730
Well, Yuzhi?

14:56.610 --> 14:58.610
My lotus congee isn't bad, is it?

14:59.490 --> 15:01.130
Do you know why I like lotus congee?

15:03.130 --> 15:04.130
When I was young, I loved sweets,

15:05.010 --> 15:06.980
yet Mother often made this for me.

15:07.580 --> 15:08.850
She said lotus seeds clear the heart,

15:09.300 --> 15:11.530
bitter at first taste, but sweet
in the aftertaste.

15:12.650 --> 15:14.250
If one only wants sweetness,

15:14.250 --> 15:15.770
pastries would do.

15:16.370 --> 15:18.180
The "Smiley" my aunt made were delicious.

15:21.530 --> 15:22.530
That lingering sweetness

15:23.180 --> 15:25.250
may not be as direct as pastries,

15:26.650 --> 15:27.730
but what if that direct sweetness

15:28.420 --> 15:29.940
lasts only for a moment?

16:00.850 --> 16:01.890
Are you out of your mind?

16:02.480 --> 16:03.340
Do you know Master

16:03.340 --> 16:04.850
and the others are searching all over for you?

16:05.250 --> 16:07.060
You said "no set meeting,"

16:08.430 --> 16:09.700
refused even to come down the mountain,

16:11.700 --> 16:12.650
and here you are,

16:12.650 --> 16:14.700
busy making lotus congee for someone.

16:18.580 --> 16:19.650
What's it to you?

16:25.010 --> 16:26.100
It concerns me.

16:27.820 --> 16:30.010
The matter of the man in black isn't
settled yet.

16:30.730 --> 16:32.010
I told you I'll find him myself.

16:33.980 --> 16:34.820
Leave now.

16:34.940 --> 16:35.890
If Master discovers you,

16:35.890 --> 16:36.730
you won't be able to leave.

16:37.130 --> 16:37.970
Why?

16:38.100 --> 16:39.130
What do you mean, why?

16:39.340 --> 16:40.700
Why did you suddenly change your mind?

16:41.490 --> 16:42.850
What did your master tell you?

16:43.940 --> 16:45.270
Is it that skin-painted demon story again?

16:47.130 --> 16:48.370
Yes, the skin-painted demon.

16:49.100 --> 16:50.250
He killed my aunt.

16:50.250 --> 16:51.730
He killed her friends.

16:51.730 --> 16:52.940
I cannot repeat her mistake.

16:56.650 --> 16:57.730
But I'm not that demon.

16:58.060 --> 16:59.010
Your aunt is your aunt.

16:59.010 --> 16:59.850
You are you.

17:00.220 --> 17:01.340
Why mix the two?

17:03.010 --> 17:03.940
How do I know you're not?

17:04.900 --> 17:06.370
The skin-painted demon excelled at disguise.

17:06.530 --> 17:07.700
When you pretended to be Chang Ning,

17:08.250 --> 17:09.220
no one noticed.

17:17.380 --> 17:18.220
Zhao,

17:18.810 --> 17:20.530
what must I do for you to believe me?

17:23.220 --> 17:24.700
If you don't want to search for
the man in black,

17:25.380 --> 17:26.250
then we won't.

17:26.770 --> 17:27.770
We can abandon everything,

17:27.900 --> 17:28.910
leave the martial world behind.

17:28.980 --> 17:30.050
I have parents, family, friends.

17:30.290 --> 17:31.900
Why should I abandon them for you?

17:32.730 --> 17:33.570
Zhao.

17:35.490 --> 17:36.330
Milady,

17:36.330 --> 17:37.290
Lord Qi is here.

17:43.010 --> 17:43.850
Master.

17:45.180 --> 17:46.220
Father. Mother.

17:46.770 --> 17:47.620
Zhao,

17:47.700 --> 17:48.740
you're too young to understand

17:49.010 --> 17:50.900
how treacherous the Demon Sect can be.

17:51.380 --> 17:52.220
Leave this matter

17:52.660 --> 17:54.140
to us adults.

17:54.620 --> 17:55.490
Mr. Mu,

17:55.490 --> 17:56.980
why aren't you out yet?

17:58.090 --> 17:59.250
I wonder

17:59.730 --> 18:01.490
what brings Lord Qi here.

18:29.250 --> 18:30.090
Where did you

18:30.570 --> 18:31.530
get this wrist guard?

18:32.900 --> 18:34.490
It's a memento from my father.

18:35.660 --> 18:36.810
Why do you ask?

18:36.810 --> 18:37.770
Lord Qi?

18:38.140 --> 18:39.900
Pingshu gave this to
the skin-painted demon.

18:40.490 --> 18:41.660
I saw it with my own eyes.

18:41.940 --> 18:43.900
So it was Mu Zhengming?

18:44.490 --> 18:45.330
Qi,

18:45.660 --> 18:46.500
what are you saying?

18:47.050 --> 18:47.890
Skin-painted demon.

18:48.330 --> 18:49.700
Your father is the skin-painted demon?

18:50.940 --> 18:51.780
Lord Qi,

18:52.380 --> 18:53.250
are you certain?

18:53.250 --> 18:54.330
I would never mistake it.

18:55.490 --> 18:56.660
The wrist guards on your arms

18:56.860 --> 18:58.090
are the best proof.

19:06.090 --> 19:06.930
Shangguan!

19:14.010 --> 19:15.540
Zhao, wait for me.

19:27.010 --> 19:27.940
Master,

19:27.940 --> 19:29.660
was Mu Zhengming truly the skin-painted demon?

19:32.010 --> 19:33.090
How could I lie

19:33.700 --> 19:34.900
about your aunt's fate?

19:37.420 --> 19:38.260
Get up.

19:40.770 --> 19:41.860
I saw

19:42.330 --> 19:43.420
that demon twice.

19:44.380 --> 19:45.660
I will never forget him.

19:48.900 --> 19:50.010
When I first met him,

19:51.180 --> 19:52.620
my cultivation was still shallow.

19:53.290 --> 19:54.660
While pursuing a villain,

19:55.380 --> 19:56.620
I fell into a trap.

19:57.730 --> 19:58.770
Your aunt rushed to save me.

19:59.380 --> 20:00.490
In the midst of the fierce battle,

20:00.810 --> 20:02.050
this man suddenly appeared

20:02.900 --> 20:04.420
and lent us his aid.

20:25.600 --> 20:26.470
What?

20:26.490 --> 20:27.570
Do you find me too ruthless?

20:27.860 --> 20:29.660
No. You are not ruthless at all.

20:29.660 --> 20:31.290
On the contrary, I think you are like

20:31.980 --> 20:32.820
wind and fire:

20:33.570 --> 20:34.570
pure as the wind,

20:34.940 --> 20:36.090
fierce as the fire.

20:36.660 --> 20:37.940
It suits you perfectly.

20:39.250 --> 20:40.900
(Righteous Spirit)
"Pure as the wind,

20:41.290 --> 20:42.700
fierce as the fire."

20:44.010 --> 20:46.050
So it was he who first said that.

20:46.050 --> 20:47.330
In this martial world,

20:48.380 --> 20:50.140
many admired your aunt.

20:50.140 --> 20:52.220
Few truly understood her.

20:52.940 --> 20:54.180
But he was different.

20:58.180 --> 21:00.570
I saw this and thought it would look lovely
on you.

21:16.050 --> 21:17.140
Irises.

21:17.530 --> 21:18.980
They'll bring good luck.

21:28.700 --> 21:29.540
Master.

21:29.730 --> 21:31.090
But Mu Qingyan told me

21:31.530 --> 21:33.620
Mu Zhengming
never left the Hanhai Mountains.

21:33.770 --> 21:36.570
How can you trust the words of

21:38.490 --> 21:39.530
It was my fault.

21:40.010 --> 21:41.220
Otherwise,

21:41.730 --> 21:43.570
your aunt would never have met him.

21:43.940 --> 21:45.090
I was blind.

21:45.700 --> 21:46.700
I failed to see

21:47.290 --> 21:50.940
that he was a fiend wearing human skin.

21:53.180 --> 21:55.620
I can't let you
walk the same path as Pingshu.

21:56.810 --> 21:57.660
From today on,

21:58.770 --> 22:01.010
you're not to take a single step
outside Qingque Sect.

22:01.980 --> 22:02.820
If you dare,

22:04.530 --> 22:06.360
don't blame me for
casting aside our master-disciple bond

22:08.620 --> 22:12.100
(Righteous Spirit)

22:16.490 --> 22:18.090
(My father could never be him.)

22:18.770 --> 22:19.770
(Knowing his character,)

22:20.220 --> 22:21.860
(he'd never do such things.)

22:25.220 --> 22:27.140
(Then who is the owner
of this wrist guard?)

22:31.490 --> 22:33.860
This is where my father lived as a child.

22:34.770 --> 22:35.730
Two cradles.

22:37.420 --> 22:38.260
Could it be...

22:38.420 --> 22:39.260
Young Master,

22:42.290 --> 22:43.130
Elder Yan has arrived.

22:43.330 --> 22:44.180
Young Master.

22:44.250 --> 22:45.860
Did my father have a brother?

22:54.590 --> 22:55.490
You...

22:55.490 --> 22:56.620
How did you know?

22:57.290 --> 22:58.130
Where is he?

23:06.490 --> 23:08.250
This was all Nie Hengcheng's doing.

23:08.660 --> 23:10.490
Back then, after your grandmother,

23:10.810 --> 23:13.490
Lady Ouyang, gave birth to twin sons,

23:13.940 --> 23:15.050
Nie Hengcheng

23:15.050 --> 23:18.180
presented the old chief with a stunning beauty.

23:18.180 --> 23:19.980
Lady Ouyang, in fury,

23:19.980 --> 23:21.050
left and insisted on

23:21.380 --> 23:24.140
taking both young masters.

23:25.010 --> 23:25.850
In the struggle,

23:26.140 --> 23:28.420
the old chief managed to keep only your father.

23:28.420 --> 23:29.330
Three years later,

23:29.330 --> 23:31.420
he found your grandmother.

23:31.420 --> 23:33.900
By then she was gravely ill, near death.

23:34.570 --> 23:35.410
She said

23:36.010 --> 23:37.250
the young master she had taken

23:37.250 --> 23:39.290
had already died of illness.

23:40.250 --> 23:42.980
The old chief was deeply shaken

23:43.250 --> 23:44.490
and soon passed away.

23:45.250 --> 23:47.140
Your father was still young,

23:47.140 --> 23:50.860
so the sect's affairs fell into
Nie Hengcheng's hands.

23:51.900 --> 23:55.330
In time, he usurped the position of Sect Chief.

24:01.860 --> 24:03.490
Eternal Sacred Sect,

24:03.490 --> 24:05.290
unify the martial world!

24:05.570 --> 24:06.980
Eternal Sacred Sect,

24:07.220 --> 24:08.700
unify the martial world!

24:08.900 --> 24:10.530
Twenty years ago,

24:11.050 --> 24:13.810
the other young master suddenly returned,

24:14.220 --> 24:15.730
seeking to reclaim his inheritance.

24:16.300 --> 24:19.740
(Mu Zhengyang, Li Sect)

24:37.220 --> 24:40.180
Nie Hengcheng claimed he was an impostor

24:40.180 --> 24:41.860
and sought to execute him.

24:42.730 --> 24:43.570
Fortunately,

24:43.940 --> 24:46.010
Young Master Zhengming intervened in time,

24:54.980 --> 24:55.980
and Nie Hengcheng spared him.

24:57.490 --> 24:59.620
At first, Nie Hengcheng refused.

24:59.980 --> 25:02.090
But your father promised him

25:02.530 --> 25:05.330
that he would never acknowledge Zhengyang.

25:05.330 --> 25:06.860
Only then were they allowed to leave.

25:07.860 --> 25:09.050
Nie Hengcheng even branded him here

25:09.050 --> 25:10.220
(Abandoned)
"Abandoned"

25:10.220 --> 25:11.490
before letting him go.

25:11.880 --> 25:12.730
And then?

25:12.730 --> 25:14.810
He likely hid deep in some remote mountains.

25:15.090 --> 25:17.860
After that, I never heard of him again.

25:19.770 --> 25:22.330
Young Master, why do you ask about this today?

25:22.900 --> 25:23.740
Uncle Cheng,

25:25.220 --> 25:26.700
Elder Yan has worked hard of late.

25:27.140 --> 25:28.180
Have someone

25:28.180 --> 25:30.290
fetch two jars of aged liquor from the cellar

25:30.940 --> 25:32.090
for him to take back.

25:32.490 --> 25:33.810
- Yes.
- Young Master...

25:33.810 --> 25:34.700
Elder Yan,

25:34.700 --> 25:35.540
please.

25:43.380 --> 25:44.220
Uncle Cheng,

25:45.220 --> 25:46.380
now it's your turn to speak.

25:48.770 --> 25:50.250
Nie Hengcheng was meticulous.

25:51.140 --> 25:52.220
He would never have allowed

25:52.220 --> 25:54.220
an ambitious Mu heir to leave freely.

25:54.530 --> 25:56.380
Father must have understood the stakes.

25:57.530 --> 25:59.330
Where did he hide Mu Zhengyang?

25:59.330 --> 26:00.490
He did indeed

26:00.490 --> 26:01.940
hide Zhengyang

26:01.940 --> 26:03.050
in a certain place.

26:03.420 --> 26:04.490
Stay here for now.

26:05.010 --> 26:05.900
Once the storm passes,

26:06.290 --> 26:07.140
I will take you away.

26:09.940 --> 26:10.780
Wait.

26:16.020 --> 26:19.380
(Abandoned)

26:19.380 --> 26:25.780
(Jiuzhou Archive)

26:30.860 --> 26:32.190
(Abandoned)
Irises.

26:32.330 --> 26:33.730
They'll bring good luck.

26:52.140 --> 26:53.000
Uncle Cheng,

26:53.090 --> 26:54.420
do you know where this man is now?

26:54.860 --> 26:55.810
He's dead.

26:55.810 --> 26:56.650
Dead?

26:57.050 --> 26:58.860
About fifteen years ago.

26:59.730 --> 27:00.570
At that time,

27:00.810 --> 27:03.010
the Young Master had moved with you
to Carefree Chamber.

27:03.900 --> 27:05.050
One day,

27:05.050 --> 27:06.140
Mr. Chang

27:06.140 --> 27:08.940
came to visit, bringing a frail young woman.

27:31.420 --> 27:32.490
Did he leave

27:33.180 --> 27:34.290
any last words?

27:37.490 --> 27:38.620
He said nothing.

27:45.290 --> 27:46.660
In a few more days,

27:47.570 --> 27:48.770
I'll be seeing him myself.

27:49.290 --> 27:50.290
I can ask for you then.

27:51.620 --> 27:52.460
Don't talk nonsense.

27:59.010 --> 27:59.940
I asked the Young Master.

28:00.770 --> 28:01.610
He said

28:01.940 --> 28:03.530
Zhengyang was already dead.

28:04.010 --> 28:04.940
That woman

28:04.940 --> 28:06.330
had only come to return his belongings.

28:07.730 --> 28:08.620
Which means

28:10.090 --> 28:12.010
no one can prove he ever existed.

28:15.380 --> 28:16.220
Uncle Cheng,

28:17.490 --> 28:18.330
did Mu Zhengyang

28:18.330 --> 28:19.330
leave behind any other relics?

28:33.810 --> 28:34.660
You're waiting for him.

28:35.810 --> 28:37.220
Master has already ordered the Six Sects:

28:38.250 --> 28:40.620
if Mu Qingyan steps out of
the Hanhai Mountains,

28:41.220 --> 28:42.290
he is not to be spared.

28:42.900 --> 28:44.730
I only hope he never comes.

28:46.380 --> 28:48.290
But these past few days, you've lingered
at Fengyun Peak.

28:48.570 --> 28:49.410
You are still waiting.

28:50.380 --> 28:51.860
How do you know where I've been?

28:52.290 --> 28:53.420
Master asked you to keep an eye on me?

28:54.490 --> 28:55.730
Everyone is worried about you.

29:02.530 --> 29:03.380
I am waiting,

29:04.380 --> 29:05.570
but I'm not waiting for him.

29:06.940 --> 29:08.180
I'm waiting for an answer.

29:12.490 --> 29:13.330
Zhao,

29:13.620 --> 29:15.010
the Ingenious Scholar said

29:15.290 --> 29:16.330
these storybooks

29:16.330 --> 29:17.660
are all the latest editions.

29:17.660 --> 29:19.020
Have a look and see if you like them.

29:22.490 --> 29:24.420
It's either a young hero meeting
a peasant girl,

29:24.900 --> 29:26.810
or a rich lady marrying a scholar,

29:27.490 --> 29:28.490
or perhaps

29:28.490 --> 29:30.090
an immortal descending to earth,

29:30.090 --> 29:31.420
stirring up life-and-death drama.

29:31.900 --> 29:32.810
I'm tired of such tales.

29:35.980 --> 29:38.050
What are these outdated stories?

29:38.490 --> 29:39.730
Our Zhao isn't a child anymore.

29:39.730 --> 29:40.900
What are you saying?

29:40.900 --> 29:42.660
I picked these out with care.

29:42.660 --> 29:44.050
All right, all right, I know, I know.

29:47.090 --> 29:48.060
Zhao, look

29:48.060 --> 29:48.950
what I have prepared for you.

29:48.960 --> 29:50.930
Something new and solid.

29:51.330 --> 29:52.980
A complete set of mechanisms:

29:53.660 --> 29:54.500
a mechanical frog,

29:55.010 --> 29:56.220
a mechanical grasshopper,

29:56.220 --> 29:57.380
and this,

29:58.570 --> 29:59.700
a mechanical bird.

29:59.700 --> 30:00.730
Quite solid, indeed.

30:00.730 --> 30:01.770
- Look.
- Madam,

30:01.770 --> 30:02.900
Mr. Chang once gave Milady

30:02.900 --> 30:04.330
a mechanical bird as well.

30:06.530 --> 30:07.370
Xiaofeng,

30:07.490 --> 30:08.730
the weather's nice.

30:08.730 --> 30:11.570
How about a walk with me?

30:11.570 --> 30:12.530
Pingchun,

30:12.530 --> 30:14.810
I heard that Yin Sulian

30:15.180 --> 30:16.330
has changed her ways lately,

30:16.330 --> 30:17.640
spending her days in the Buddha hall,

30:17.640 --> 30:18.910
eating vegetarian and chanting sutras.

30:19.290 --> 30:20.220
Shall we

30:20.220 --> 30:21.140
go take a look at her?

30:21.140 --> 30:22.490
- Sure, let's go.
- Let's go take a look.

30:22.490 --> 30:23.820
- Father, Mother.
- Come, Zhao.

30:24.620 --> 30:25.660
Don't worry.

30:26.050 --> 30:27.700
I won't repeat Aunt's mistake.

30:29.220 --> 30:30.620
If he's someone I shouldn't love,

30:31.290 --> 30:32.250
then from now on,

30:33.660 --> 30:34.660
I won't.

30:36.490 --> 30:37.330
Zhao,

30:37.490 --> 30:38.530
you've always had your own mind,

30:38.900 --> 30:39.770
bold enough to act your way.

30:40.380 --> 30:41.580
Forget that skin-painted demon's son.

30:42.530 --> 30:43.370
Forget him.

30:48.570 --> 30:50.140
Reading some old clich├ęs now and then

30:50.140 --> 30:51.380
isn't so bad.

30:51.380 --> 30:52.290
Thank you, Father.

30:52.290 --> 30:53.130
Thank you, Mother.

31:10.070 --> 31:10.940
Young Master,

31:10.940 --> 31:12.010
we've searched everywhere.

31:12.010 --> 31:13.730
There's truly no trace of the relic
from those years.

31:15.530 --> 31:17.050
(If Mu Zhengyang was the skin-painted demon,)

31:18.490 --> 31:19.330
(then...)

31:19.810 --> 31:20.770
My aunt came here?

31:21.140 --> 31:22.660
She was searching for the saliva as well.

31:23.090 --> 31:24.330
With her

31:24.860 --> 31:26.220
was a masked man.

31:26.700 --> 31:27.540
This painting

31:28.140 --> 31:29.730
was done by him.

31:36.180 --> 31:37.860
What unique wrist guards,

31:38.140 --> 31:39.250
embroidered with two

31:39.940 --> 31:40.780
irises.

31:42.620 --> 31:43.460
Irises.

32:37.660 --> 32:38.500
Young Master,

32:40.810 --> 32:41.650
where are you going?

32:41.810 --> 32:42.650
Qingque Sect.

32:43.530 --> 32:44.370
She's waiting for me.

32:44.490 --> 32:45.330
Young Master,

32:46.090 --> 32:47.380
since Elder Hu was abducted,

32:47.770 --> 32:49.570
many former members of the Xuanwu Altar
have defected.

32:49.570 --> 32:50.590
Morale in the sect is unstable.

32:50.810 --> 32:52.180
How can you leave at a time like this?

32:54.570 --> 32:55.940
Since when did my affairs

32:57.530 --> 32:58.770
become yours to manage?

32:58.770 --> 32:59.730
In your eyes, Young Master,

33:00.420 --> 33:01.530
is there only Miss Cai?

33:01.530 --> 33:02.530
Is there no place for us?

33:02.900 --> 33:04.090
Even if you won't think of us,

33:04.490 --> 33:05.590
at least think of your own safety.

33:05.900 --> 33:07.380
Qingque Sect is a deadly trap right now.

33:07.380 --> 33:08.420
If you go,

33:08.420 --> 33:09.490
your chances are slim.

33:09.900 --> 33:10.740
Perhaps

33:10.940 --> 33:12.620
we can send word by other means.

33:12.620 --> 33:13.900
I must go in person.

33:14.330 --> 33:15.620
Nie Zhe is watching like a hawk.

33:16.290 --> 33:17.940
If anything happens to you,

33:17.940 --> 33:18.900
then the sect chief's seat...

33:18.900 --> 33:20.220
Then it changes hands again.

33:21.810 --> 33:22.650
Whatever you do.

33:43.260 --> 33:44.300
(Past and Future Glory)

33:44.330 --> 33:45.220
A spy reports

33:45.620 --> 33:47.700
"Strengthen defenses"
Mu Qingyan has left the Hanhai Mountains.

33:48.250 --> 33:49.140
Even if

33:49.140 --> 33:50.250
he has,

33:51.180 --> 33:52.770
he may not dare come to Qingque Sect.

33:54.490 --> 33:56.770
We're on full alert.

33:56.770 --> 33:58.810
He must know that.

33:58.810 --> 34:00.140
If this Young Master Mu

34:01.090 --> 34:02.730
knew when to retreat,

34:03.250 --> 34:05.010
he wouldn't have challenged Nie Zhe alone

34:05.010 --> 34:06.090
in the first place,

34:06.090 --> 34:07.530
nor reclaimed the Demon Sect

34:08.170 --> 34:09.570
by his own strength.

34:09.980 --> 34:11.260
If I'm not mistaken,

34:12.210 --> 34:13.740
he'll come up the mountain tonight.

34:13.740 --> 34:14.900
If he dares come,

34:15.210 --> 34:17.050
he won't leave alive.

34:18.490 --> 34:19.570
It's just Zhao...

34:38.570 --> 34:39.410
Zhao.

34:42.050 --> 34:42.890
Zhao.

34:45.740 --> 34:46.580
Mother.

34:47.130 --> 34:48.570
Come with me somewhere.

34:59.380 --> 35:00.900
With this broken body of mine,

35:01.610 --> 35:02.530
I'm afraid I cannot go.

35:02.780 --> 35:03.620
Back then,

35:04.420 --> 35:06.650
Zigui was closest to you.

35:07.170 --> 35:08.860
This time, you must escort his ashes

35:08.860 --> 35:09.700
back to Jiangdong.

35:11.090 --> 35:11.930
Even if

35:12.170 --> 35:13.210
we have to carry you.

35:16.610 --> 35:17.450
Zhao,

35:17.860 --> 35:19.380
stay here tonight.

35:19.380 --> 35:20.940
Help your Uncle Lei pack.

35:20.940 --> 35:21.980
We leave tomorrow.

35:24.210 --> 35:25.050
I'm not going.

35:29.780 --> 35:30.620
Lei Xiuming,

35:30.980 --> 35:33.010
it's been eighteen years.

35:33.530 --> 35:35.570
The one who harmed you has been found.

35:35.570 --> 35:36.820
Are you going to hide on this mountain

35:36.820 --> 35:37.980
for the rest of your life?

35:37.980 --> 35:38.820
Uncle Lei,

35:40.210 --> 35:41.490
was it Mu Zhengming

35:41.980 --> 35:42.980
who ambushed you back then?

35:46.050 --> 35:46.900
It was too dark.

35:48.690 --> 35:50.210
Everything happened too fast.

35:51.690 --> 35:52.650
I couldn't see clearly.

35:53.900 --> 35:54.740
Enough.

35:54.940 --> 35:56.490
Don't bring up the past again.

37:15.780 --> 37:17.530
Who would have thought the dignified

37:18.740 --> 37:20.300
Qingque Sect would use Thunderstorms?

37:20.610 --> 37:21.740
Back then, Qingque Sect

37:22.530 --> 37:24.340
confiscated many of them.

37:25.570 --> 37:26.820
But the explosives are too vicious,

37:27.130 --> 37:28.050
too underhanded,

37:28.530 --> 37:30.300
so the sect disdained to use them.

37:31.130 --> 37:32.300
Today, however,

37:32.300 --> 37:33.980
they're perfectly suited

37:34.380 --> 37:35.820
for Young Master Mu.

37:37.740 --> 37:38.900
Mu Qingyan,

37:38.900 --> 37:41.050
knowing it's a trap and still daring to come,

37:41.050 --> 37:42.300
you've got nerve.

37:43.610 --> 37:44.570
Where is Zhao?

37:45.050 --> 37:46.210
She won't see you.

37:46.820 --> 37:47.660
I advise you

37:47.940 --> 37:49.650
to surrender now.

37:50.900 --> 37:52.490
Enough talk.

38:51.740 --> 38:52.860
You won't see her.

38:55.530 --> 38:57.010
Let's see how long you can hold out.

39:09.490 --> 39:10.380
Yunke,

39:10.980 --> 39:12.690
the boy is stalling.

39:25.490 --> 39:26.330
Zhao.

39:26.610 --> 39:27.450
What is it?

39:30.050 --> 39:30.890
Nothing.

39:32.630 --> 39:33.490
Forget it.

39:33.490 --> 39:34.530
Stop drinking tea.

39:34.530 --> 39:35.900
Go help Uncle Lei pack.

39:35.900 --> 39:37.610
Leave the jars and bottles,

39:37.610 --> 39:38.650
just pack some clothes.

39:59.130 --> 39:59.970
Mother.

40:01.130 --> 40:01.970
What now?

40:02.530 --> 40:03.570
I want to go back.

40:07.010 --> 40:08.340
Back for what?

40:08.650 --> 40:09.530
Feicui has

40:09.820 --> 40:11.490
already packed your things.

40:11.690 --> 40:12.740
Running back and forth

40:13.130 --> 40:13.970
is such a bother.

40:18.050 --> 40:19.420
Zhao, don't go.

40:21.530 --> 40:22.820
Has he come?

40:31.090 --> 40:32.820
You lured me away on purpose.

40:36.860 --> 40:38.210
You're planning

40:41.380 --> 40:43.300
to ambush and kill him.

40:46.610 --> 40:47.450
Zhao,

40:47.690 --> 40:49.570
your master and the others are furious.

40:49.820 --> 40:50.660
Besides,

40:50.900 --> 40:52.130
Young Master Mu is highly skilled.

40:52.610 --> 40:54.210
He may have already escaped.

40:54.690 --> 40:55.820
If he doesn't see me,

40:57.420 --> 40:58.490
he won't leave.

41:00.090 --> 41:00.930
Zhao.

41:02.400 --> 41:03.260
Zhao!

41:03.260 --> 41:04.650
They said it was all in the past,

41:05.490 --> 41:06.740
but it's not over yet.

41:16.010 --> 41:16.850
Stop!

41:20.130 --> 41:20.970
Zhao!

41:25.120 --> 41:35.780
=Generation to Generation=

41:54.540 --> 41:58.950
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

41:59.515 --> 42:04.130
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

42:04.470 --> 42:09.035
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

42:09.560 --> 42:13.860
♪Free to wander in the world♪

42:16.805 --> 42:21.505
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

42:22.030 --> 42:26.320
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

42:26.980 --> 42:31.010
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

42:31.325 --> 42:36.450
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

42:37.025 --> 42:41.835
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

42:42.050 --> 42:46.220
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

42:46.945 --> 42:50.880
♪I freely roam in the world♪

42:51.380 --> 42:56.655
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

43:19.385 --> 43:24.515
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

43:24.880 --> 43:29.250
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

43:29.515 --> 43:33.645
♪I freely roam in the world♪

43:33.830 --> 43:39.405
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
